+## Layer 11 — The tepui-thread vs. broader CoO
+
+The tepui-thread is **a coherent strand** within CoO's larger universe — it does not replace existing systems but layers a unifying cosmology over them. Specifically:
+
+**What inherits from existing CoO:**
+- The Rot Choir, Palimpsest, Pale Curation, Saccharine Concord (existed pre-thread)
+- The combat system, skill trees, weapon mechanics (existing infrastructure)
