+> 1. What was the Felling?
+> 2. What is the First Root?
+> 3. What is Urqu?
+> 4. What are the three endings?
+>
+> Later documents build from this spine and also settle questions this phase deliberately left open. **Six major creative bets are preserved below as the Phase 1 decision record.**
