+- **Whether ambient everyday-binding has a measurable Thinning effect** or is purely flavor — soft lean: a faint real trickle (so depopulated/despairing regions, where no one conjures flowers anymore, thin faster — a haunting texture). Implementation may keep it flavor-only for simplicity.
+- **The magic diag-category schema.** Engineering.
